There once was a boy named harry destined to be a star. His parents were killed by voldemort who left him with a lightning scar. Harry goes to Hogwarts where he meets Ron and Hermione. Mcgonagall requires him to play for Gryffindor. Draco is a Daddy's boy. Quirrel becomes unemployed. The sorcerer stone is destroyed by Dumbledore. Ron breaks his wand. Now Giny's gone, and Harry is in mortal danger. Tom Riddle hides his snake inside his ginormous secret chamber. Harry blows up at Aunt Marge, the dementors come and take charge. Lupin is a wolf, the rat is a man and now the prisoner is at large. They use time travel so they can save the prisoner of Azkaban who just happens to be harry's god father.